longBusinessSummary: Trek Resources, Inc., an independent energy company, engages in the exploration, development, exploitation, and acquisition of onshore oil and natural gas properties principally in the United States. The company was formerly known as McGowen Resources Company, Inc. and changed its name to Trek Resources, Inc. in 2001. Trek Resources was incorporated in 1983 and is based in Dallas, Texas.
